Add guarded Supabase client factories (browser anon + server service-role),
full Postgres schema with RLS for customers/orders/order_items/payments/
quotes/abandoned_carts/news_posts, and env template entries. The public
site keeps working with no Supabase config; persistence degrades gracefully.
---
 .env.example        |  15 ++++
 lib/supabase.ts     |  52 ++++++++++++++
 package.json        |   1 +
 supabase/schema.sql | 166 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 4 files changed, 234 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 lib/supabase.ts
 create mode 100644 supabase/schema.sql

